{
  "stem": "3631.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- it rained into the-- into the cattle cars, and which we didn't mind it, really, because we were free.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What's a little rain to us?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and from Munich, we went to Mittenwalde, a town in-- in upper Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were, again, in three days in a transit camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, we went by train, via Innsbruck, the Brenner Pass, to Bologna, where we spent two days.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was another incident on this, near-- near Verona.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The train stopped overnight on the track.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we didn't have much food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some young fellows started scouting out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and they came across a farm.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the farm had a barn full of peaches that were too ripe-- too ripe to be sold.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the farmer gave us permission to take the peaches.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Meanwhile, the whole train, it-- with bags, whatever bags we had, went to that farm.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We filled everything up with peaches, that we can.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was the most delicious peaches we ever had in our life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Many of us had a bad belly ache, too, after that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were not used to this food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But it was one of the incidents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The whole trip into Italy was a great experience, because we were free.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The-- the cattle cars did not have any barbed wire on it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The-- the-- the doors were open.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Every couple of hours, in a free and open country, the train would stop, blow the whistle.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Everybody would jump off the train, disappear in the bushes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And after five minutes, they would blow the whistle again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Everybody got back into the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And it's not always easy to get into a cattle car.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I almost missed the train once on one of these occasions.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But that was nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
